.DT
set_stopped
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_stopped

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_stopped -  This method sets the stopped attribute of the map handler.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_stopped(int s)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^s%^RESET%^ - the new value of the stopped flag

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the stopped attribute of the map handler.
If the stopped attribute is non-zero then the map handler will
stop processing the currently queued rooms.
.EP

